'''Abda of Edessa''' was a bishop of [[Edessa, Mesopotamia|Edessa]] in the [[Church of the East]]. He is commemorated as a [[saint]] by that church with a [[feast day]] of February 16.
==References== Holweck, F. G. ''A Biographical Dictionary of the Saints''. St. Louis, MO: B. Herder Book Co., 1924.
